{"tid":2403083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旅發局邀居港外籍人士宣傳來港旅遊","createTime":"2021-02-11T01:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T02:01:55.000Z","uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4e506830d28f9ba8b5116144c4053b0526e0e59c","tid":2403083,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:27:57.000Z","msg":"旅發局啟動宣傳活動，邀請逾220名居港外籍人士加入「Hong Kong Super Fans」，透過不同活動推廣香港，鼓勵其海外親友能在疫情過後來港旅遊。獲邀人士分別來自亞洲、大洋洲、歐洲及美洲，旅發局期望他們可推介本港美食、藝術、地道文化及郊野風光等最新資訊。當局並將為其安排不同活動，首項是參與以新春為主題的網上導賞團，了解港人過農曆新年的習俗。<br />\n<br />\n當局並透過全球辦事處邀請20個客源市場人士參與相關活動。未來亦會邀請來自內地、東南亞、日本、南韓、澳洲、歐美的媒體參加導賞團。"},{"pid":"b96c4cae4416518b268e96c3fc812276245e1b58","tid":2403083,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:29:20.000Z","msg":"一定要搞反宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7e609e883d3ed57437d4ddfab405833667f0a1","tid":2403083,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"你放多d asian tight free pussies 係中環灣仔咪有鬼佬黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c224428fbb173e296b3fba01715ca470d8f656c0","tid":2403083,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:30:23.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43a5b558c9aafb0362dbfa1ec8c25df7563f1ae","tid":2403083,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:30:35.000Z","msg":"港共 *hidden agenda：要人質要脅外國"},{"pid":"a12b8bac4d569fb28a543bf3ae67758c4f8b04a1","tid":2403083,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:33:06.000Z","msg":"如果搵逃輝宣傳仲邊會有人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306b1037c8936795a10b1d367f6c9c3c43723d72","tid":2403083,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"叫陶輝同莊定賢就得啦<img src=\"/asset